      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，这是一个Access-Based的模型。我理解为：用户先登录，拿到令牌，再用令牌去请求资源。中间需要加Application这个环节吗，还是用户直接拿token找资源服务器？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Identity Provider",
        "Access Token",
        "Application",
        "Resource Server"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "需要Application节点。实际流程是用户通过Identity Provider登录后，token是发给Application的，然后Application拿着token去请求Resource Server。这样更符合真实架构。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Application",
        "Access Token",
        "Resource Server"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主流程画出来：User → Identity Provider → Application → Resource Server，用Login和Access Token标注好交互关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Identity Provider",
        "Application",
